male imago. A. dorsal view; B. forewing; C. hind wing; D. half of genitalia in ventral view; E. half of genitalia in ventrolateral view; F. half of genitalia in lateral view; G. penis ventral view - twisted in stereoscope (paratype); H. genitalia in ventral view; I. genitalia in lateral view. (eco = expansion curved outwards).
